      "text": "……そういえば、{user}さん\nあの時……I-UNITYのファイナルの時ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Speaking of which‚ Manager-san‚\nback then… during the I-UNITY finals‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
