      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "急にマイクが復活したじゃないですか\nあれ、なんでなのかって……考えたりしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the mics suddenly came back on‚ didn’t they?\nDid you… ever wonder why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.058803886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、みんなで考えて……\nもしかしたらって話してたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We talked about it with everyone…\nand we were wondering if…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたらあの時……\nお姉ちゃんが助けてくれたのかな、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were thinking… maybe back then…\n…maybe my sister helped us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……なんで、そう思ったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why did you think that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "音響ブースの配線がおかしいことに気付けた時\nなんとなく、お姉ちゃんの声が聞こえた気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I realized there was something wrong with the wiring in the sound booth‚\nI felt like I could hear my sister's voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないって\n信じてもらえないと思ってます……でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know it sounds crazy‚\nand I think you might not believe me… but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私もステージに立っていた時\n聞こえた気がするんです……「心配ないよ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was standing on stage‚\nI thought I heard it too… \"Don't worry.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、二人にも……\nやっぱりあれは、空耳なんかじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ both of you…\nSo that wasn't just our imagination…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、なんでもない。その話、俺も信じるよ\n麻奈ならあの状況、黙って見過ごせなかっただろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it's nothing. I believe you.\nIf it were Mana‚ she wouldn't have just stood by and watched‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、俺達のことを助けてくれたんだろう\nあいつはそういうやつだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and she must have helped us.\nThat's the kind of person she is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
